Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.20,0:00:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七宫？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.88,0:00:06.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样…不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.71,0:00:09.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.81,0:00:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有恋爱经验的我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.62,0:00:17.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于这种事情一直很迟钝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.29,0:00:19.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七宫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.90,0:00:24.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是这样的我 当看到她流下眼泪之时也发觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.38,0:00:27.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七宫到底是在和什么做斗争
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.21,0:00:29.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么问我那种问题
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.99,0:00:31.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会想说那样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.93,0:00:36.43,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水魔导师的攻击变强大了 请求救援
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.88,0:00:38.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有她哭泣的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.54,0:00:47.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.10,0:00:51.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新发现 现在准备开始探索
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.64,0:00:52.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.89,0:00:54.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没有带伞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.56,0:00:56.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为樟叶…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.59,0:00:58.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会和樟叶扯上关系
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.98,0:01:00.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦 快进来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.64,0:01:02.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体都变凉了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.80,0:01:06.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑暗住民的体温本来就是这么…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OP----
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【OP】
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.58,0:01:15.38,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}I wanna fallin' LOVE.....
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.42,0:01:32.05,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}予感--… 夢が続く
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.54,0:01:37.90,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}約束しても　心がどこかで怯えてるみたい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.50,0:01:41.00,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}ひとりじゃないって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.27,0:01:43.75,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}信じたいのに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.05,0:01:49.46,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}思い続けてる だけで幸せなんて言えないね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.64,0:01:55.26,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}虚ろな自信背負っていても　君が笑う
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.62,0:02:01.39,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}そして私の勇気になる 一つの言葉で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.52,0:02:03.99,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}君の世界を変えられたら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.29,0:02:08.52,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}二つの恋が進化する
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.82,0:02:12.74,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}ホントだよ　巡らせた迷いが
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.79,0:02:15.09,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}見つけた答えは
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.43,0:02:17.97,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}いつでも君に導かれた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.02,0:02:22.50,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}届ける覚悟が 様にならなくても
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.68,0:02:25.26,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}素直に伝えたい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.26,0:02:27.91,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}ココロアルガママコエガキラメク
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.10,0:02:29.19,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}Real come on voice
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.42,0:02:33.70,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}響き渡るよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.42,0:01:32.05,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}预感--… 梦想延续
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.54,0:01:37.90,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}尽管许下约定 心中某处依旧胆怯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.50,0:01:41.00,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}你不是一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.27,0:01:43.75,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}明明想要这样相信
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.05,0:01:49.46,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}思念不断滋生 但是却无法说出幸福二字
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.64,0:01:55.26,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}虽背负着虚无的自信 你依然嘴角上扬
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.62,0:02:01.39,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}你的一句话就能成为我的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.52,0:02:03.99,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}若能改变你的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.29,0:02:08.52,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}就能进化成为两份爱恋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.82,0:02:12.74,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}真的哦 冥思苦想依旧迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.79,0:02:15.09,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}最终找到的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.43,0:02:17.97,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}无论何时都能引领着你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.02,0:02:22.50,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}就算没有做好能够传达给你的觉悟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.68,0:02:25.26,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}大声地说出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.26,0:02:27.91,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}心灵深处的声音熠熠生辉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.42,0:02:33.70,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}响亮地传达给他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.13,0:02:54.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我进来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.03,0:02:56.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做了点菜粥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.89,0:02:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微吃点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.36,0:03:03.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)\pos(608,318)\3c&H000000&\fs29}Episode XI 苍月下的…最终决战
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.36,0:03:03.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)\pos(664,288)\3c&H000000&\fs21}Blue moon·Ragnarok
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.46,0:03:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微坐起来一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.17,0:03:09.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现实世界出现了歪曲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.78,0:03:12.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为邪王真眼的力量也在减弱…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.02,0:03:13.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.93,0:03:18.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来烧还是没退下去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.94,0:03:21.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也给我乖乖在家睡觉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.50,0:03:24.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.88,0:03:27.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你啊 都已经感冒了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.27,0:03:30.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天还勉强自己想到外面去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.47,0:03:32.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快就觉得头晕了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.20,0:03:35.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界要消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.20,0:03:35.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(451,438)\fs21}Vanishiment
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.80,0:03:36.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.89,0:03:38.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡了一晚已经得到完全恢复
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.73,0:03:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 直到病好为止都不准你出去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.33,0:03:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 你到底是想去哪里呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.57,0:03:45.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个我不能回答你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.31,0:03:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之前应该也说过
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.18,0:03:49.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以闇炎之主的身份提问
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.37,0:03:50.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底打算去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.86,0:03:57.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我问完之后也不打算责怪你什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.32,0:03:59.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是很讨厌这种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.20,0:04:03.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六花对我有所隐瞒而去其他地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.02,0:04:06.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.84,0:04:10.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真相很快就会昭然于天下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.87,0:04:15.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人 为什么要撇下凸守我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.46,0:04:17.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变成这幅样子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.31,0:04:18.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,de…death
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.95,0:04:20.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她还没有死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.20,0:04:21.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就会好了对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.07,0:04:23.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你那么介意的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.10,0:04:25.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我随时都可以依靠邪王真眼的力量恢复健康
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.01,0:04:26.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.80,0:04:28.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.13,0:04:35.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道必须要服下盛开于邪王崖暗黑壁之巅的黑龙花才能痊愈吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.35,0:04:38.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别随意添加设定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.73,0:04:39.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你站得那么近小心被传染啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.03,0:04:41.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人 等着我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.66,0:04:43.95,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凸守我一定会…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.76,0:04:43.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你们两位
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.10,0:04:45.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是待得太久也有被传染的危险
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.89,0:04:47.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.68,0:04:52.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见 奇美拉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.54,0:04:54.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要快点恢复哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.18,0:04:55.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作业堆了很多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.85,0:04:58.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚刚说出了禁言
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.94,0:04:59.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么！？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.60,0:05:01.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘了作业会皱眉头哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.86,0:05:03.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 索菲娅呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.00,0:05:09.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好几次想通过电子音信识别信号与她联络
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.30,0:05:11.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是却从来没得到她的回应
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.58,0:05:13.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 到底怎么回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.11,0:05:16.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙好像说她很忙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.22,0:05:17.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很容易就能看出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.62,0:05:22.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七宫说了要开始战争的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.76,0:05:25.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就猜到大概就会发展到这个地步
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.80,0:05:27.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么丹谷生你是发现了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.06,0:05:29.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一眼就发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.14,0:05:32.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个孩子眼里就只有你一个人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.28,0:05:36.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实是十花姐告诉我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.45,0:05:38.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那这之后你打算怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.60,0:05:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算是指…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.82,0:05:41.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能对那个孩子坐视不管吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.90,0:05:44.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她那么喜欢你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.58,0:05:46.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你突然这么跟我说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.88,0:05:48.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道该怎么做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.77,0:05:50.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她甚至也从来没有跟我说过那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.75,0:05:53.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么突然变得这么正经了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.77,0:05:55.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是在说实话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.72,0:05:56.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么做才好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.83,0:05:57.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.58,0:05:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女生应该比较更了解恋爱这回事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.91,0:06:02.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么会知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.52,0:06:05.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在回避吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.60,0:06:07.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有刻意回避哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.77,0:06:08.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就别插手这件事了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.56,0:06:12.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六花那个时候也是 总是发生什么立刻就…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.37,0:06:14.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是因为看富樫你们很烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.01,0:06:16.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才来帮助你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.73,0:06:19.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可没记得有拜托过你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.77,0:06:20.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.99,0:06:22.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就随你便吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.50,0:06:23.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茴香学姐 我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.42,0:06:38.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.39,0:06:39.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.58,0:06:41.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么的话你不要把人撞倒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.38,0:06:43.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么但是什么都有！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.84,0:06:43.52,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是凸守吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.38,0:06:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七宫？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.50,0:06:52.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.29,0:06:53.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在做什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.14,0:06:59.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功归来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.91,0:07:01.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.25,0:07:02.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一不小心你就死了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.52,0:07:07.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果要战胜内在的自己 就需要波纹和魔法能量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.98,0:07:09.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.21,0:07:10.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要这么轻易赞同啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.76,0:07:13.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏这个这次我也成功打败敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.76,0:07:15.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,取得了最终胜利哟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.51,0:07:20.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今往后 我就是魔法魔王少女改+α外传了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.87,0:07:23.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么有种续篇继续烂牌游戏的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.37,0:07:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此以前的事以后已经全部被我遗弃到了无知的尽头
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.22,0:07:30.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,统统消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.34,0:07:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七宫 这样真的可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.01,0:07:39.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.34,0:07:42.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.08,0:07:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是天使的反应
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.57,0:07:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,富樫同学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.65,0:07:51.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.52,0:07:53.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你该不会把她刚才的话当真
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.70,0:07:57.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想着「太好了 好像她没事」之类的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.36,0:07:58.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.24,0:08:01.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.08,0:08:03.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能 她只是在逞强
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.67,0:08:05.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事怎么可能看得出来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.18,0:08:06.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然看得出来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.34,0:08:09.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和七宫的交情也不是这一两天的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.01,0:08:12.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…你要我到底怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.88,0:08:13.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.97,0:08:16.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俗话说恋情如梦嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.66,0:08:17.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是梦的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.81,0:08:20.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随着时间的流逝应该会慢慢地醒过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.91,0:08:24.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果要强行叫醒她的话 反而会让她觉得痛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.66,0:08:29.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茴香学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.42,0:08:32.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.51,0:08:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 这不关你事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.58,0:08:37.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.51,0:08:39.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实小森大人她最喜欢你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.47,0:08:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢小六花 小凸守还有富樫同学 小七宫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.72,0:08:48.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她最喜欢中二病了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.66,0:08:52.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都觉得羡慕她呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.73,0:08:54.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我是中二病就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.08,0:08:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐你那么想？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.22,0:08:59.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话 我就能和大家分享同一种感觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.02,0:09:03.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是也不是那么容易就能变成中二病的对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.46,0:09:06.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从你开始憧憬的那一刻开始
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.85,0:09:08.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是一名堂堂正正的中二病了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.61,0:09:09.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.86,0:09:12.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茴香学姐你不是第二代邪王真眼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.38,0:09:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森夏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.38,0:09:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,438)\fs21}Mori Summer
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.70,0:09:33.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索菲亚 你好像处于迷茫之中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.11,0:09:35.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了 这么突然
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.64,0:09:38.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你已经取回你的记忆了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.52,0:09:40.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要吃药草吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.91,0:09:41.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不要啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.63,0:09:44.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想着这样比较容易对你传达我的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.97,0:09:46.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才特地换衣服过来的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.21,0:09:48.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这裙子可是很紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.02,0:09:52.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索菲亚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.57,0:09:55.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有箴言相赠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.60,0:09:57.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是魔法师 森夏的箴言
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.60,0:09:57.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(457,438)\fs21}Mori Summer
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.82,0:10:01.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森夏以前曾与冒名之人战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.82,0:10:01.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(275,438)\fs21}Mori Summer
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.05,0:10:03.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且对他们降下了惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.97,0:10:05.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时 我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.46,0:10:11.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何面对自己体内的另一个自己并与之对战的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.12,0:10:13.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一个…自己？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.24,0:10:18.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 为了了解自己 应该将目光转向外面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.15,0:10:22.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像我经由与冒牌货的对战 得以了解自己一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.90,0:10:25.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索菲亚你也有不得不战的对手才对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.40,0:10:27.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请去寻找那个对手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.69,0:10:29.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森夏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.69,0:10:29.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,438)\fs21}Mori Summer
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.87,0:10:32.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时 你的前途将会一片光明吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.43,0:10:34.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.75,0:10:38.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是麻烦啊 你懂了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.29,0:10:40.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森夏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.29,0:10:40.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,438)\fs21}Mori Summer
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.46,0:10:43.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 我帮你补充魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.26,0:10:45.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好近啊 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.93,0:10:46.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.35,0:10:48.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷霆战锤使
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.35,0:10:48.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,438)\fs21}Mjolnir Hammer
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.69,0:10:49.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点过来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.19,0:10:56.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不仅对闇炎之主出手 还把魔爪伸向了冒牌森大人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.35,0:10:58.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.18,0:11:05.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.86,0:11:07.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樟叶 月亮出来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.46,0:11:09.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是漂亮的满月哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.13,0:11:11.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说今晚是苍月呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.18,0:11:13.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍蓝…之月
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.65,0:11:18.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七宫喜欢我 但是我对六花…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.52,0:11:21.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不懂 太复杂了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.21,0:11:22.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底该怎么办…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.47,0:11:26.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七宫…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.09,0:11:29.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇者…不
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.75,0:11:31.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闇炎之主
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.78,0:11:34.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要看看我的魔法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.37,0:11:45.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七宫…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.46,0:11:46.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我寻找了很久
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.51,0:11:50.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我的对手果然只有勇者你一个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.23,0:11:52.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能这样做一个了结
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.38,0:11:53.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.74,0:11:56.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是战争！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.19,0:11:58.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.23,0:11:58.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.43,0:12:00.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔王认证
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.30,0:12:02.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.39,0:12:03.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七宫…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.80,0:12:06.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 六花不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.75,0:12:09.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才稍微不注意她就…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.19,0:12:10.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.49,0:12:12.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.97,0:12:13.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七宫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.31,0:12:18.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚有苍月对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.08,0:12:21.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概 她已经注意到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.25,0:12:24.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚是苍蓝之月的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.29,0:12:26.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍蓝之月？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.86,0:12:29.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的记不得了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.41,0:12:35.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.30,0:12:40.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗炎龙？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.63,0:12:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇者你曾经说过
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.08,0:12:47.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉睡在自己体内的暗炎龙又会苏醒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.02,0:12:49.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也希望它能被人唤醒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.17,0:12:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来自几经风霜的过去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.73,0:12:56.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未来永恒不变的绝对契约者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.56,0:13:01.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使超越时间 超越次元 前往平行世界的彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.08,0:13:03.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也意欲继续契约
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.70,0:13:07.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以其绝对的力量出现在我面前的存在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.37,0:13:12.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾错误地降生到这个混沌不堪的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.13,0:13:16.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因其强大的封印之力以及其篡改记忆的尝试
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.82,0:13:19.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己真正的记忆正在逐渐被剥夺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.20,0:13:23.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾恐怕在不久的将来会化归虚无
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.58,0:13:27.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以吾托付给汝 遥远的汝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.71,0:13:29.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将寄宿我体内的暗炎龙…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.67,0:13:32.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让它的身姿在这个世界现身的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.85,0:13:37.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吞噬 改变 重铸这个错误的世界的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.91,0:13:41.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,复活暗炎龙的钥匙有三个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.14,0:13:45.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯库尔德
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.22,0:13:49.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薇儿丹蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.91,0:13:52.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兀儿德
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.14,0:13:52.53,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs21}注：北欧神话中的诺恩三女神，是北欧神话中的命运女神。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.48,0:13:55.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是我绝对的契约者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.60,0:13:58.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是有着与我共命运的力量之人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.34,0:14:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收集这三个钥匙应该不在话下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.69,0:14:04.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾之永远契约者啊 我将会等待那个时刻的到来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.90,0:14:06.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时步入沉睡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.12,0:14:08.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在终将到来的苍蓝之月夜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.25,0:14:11.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你能将那力量交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.48,0:14:17.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就是…隐藏的地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.25,0:14:21.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然记得不太清楚 大概就在这附近
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.98,0:14:27.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…有人挖的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.85,0:14:32.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.04,0:14:34.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是邪王真眼放在这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.49,0:14:36.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.55,0:14:38.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是找过这里的标记
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.89,0:14:40.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该不会…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.04,0:14:42.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.61,0:14:44.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也找过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.73,0:14:47.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么都找不到兀儿德
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.31,0:14:49.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是送往过去的钥匙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.21,0:14:53.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了将钥匙送往过去 只能使用平行世界了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.40,0:14:57.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那张笔记里提到的平行世界的入口
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.39,0:14:59.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在第十四个铁塔所指向的阴影之下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.30,0:15:03.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我不知道那是从哪里开始数的第十四个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.25,0:15:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了找到那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.54,0:15:06.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就这样一点一滴地彻查
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.42,0:15:17.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉…但是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.03,0:15:19.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「真相很快就会昭然于天下」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.43,0:15:22.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙…一直为了这个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.25,0:15:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想起来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.11,0:15:29.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,模模糊糊地
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.75,0:15:31.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这附近的风景我有印象
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.55,0:15:36.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这边
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.25,0:15:41.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六花…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.21,0:15:45.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 无论何时都那么认真地去中二
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.39,0:15:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论何时都那么认真地去恋爱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.22,0:15:51.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都在为我着想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.27,0:15:55.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六花 六花 六花
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.04,0:15:57.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇者…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.10,0:16:06.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六花！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.20,0:16:10.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇太？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.75,0:16:14.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.58,0:16:16.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇太 这个就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.27,0:16:25.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兀儿德？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.25,0:16:26.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.26,0:16:30.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明明感冒了 还来找这种东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.81,0:16:32.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是恶化了怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.53,0:16:35.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为必须由绝对的契约者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.52,0:16:38.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远的契约者来唤醒…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.39,0:16:39.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.91,0:16:42.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是勇太的永远的契约者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.93,0:16:44.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 必须找出来才行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.08,0:16:46.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找出来 将它作为证明…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.24,0:16:52.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇太？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.02,0:16:54.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.58,0:16:56.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事不用做也没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.09,0:16:57.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.38,0:17:02.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明是契约者 却连一把钥匙都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.14,0:17:04.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是索菲亚却…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.67,0:17:05.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.70,0:17:08.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.06,0:17:11.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇太…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.20,0:17:17.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇太是我的契约者？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.26,0:17:21.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 是你绝对的契约者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.90,0:17:34.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在国中二年级的时候骨折了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.02,0:17:36.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然把它塞进那时的石膏里面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.32,0:17:40.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时的我 居然还做了这么麻烦的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.22,0:17:42.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.41,0:17:52.75,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水与柱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.62,0:17:53.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.04,0:17:55.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅此而已的话 谁都看不懂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.63,0:17:59.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在金属上面刻字很麻烦 所以中途就放弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.26,0:18:06.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是很多年前放在这儿的东西 居然还在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.21,0:18:10.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明只是块石头而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.25,0:18:14.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是唤醒暗炎龙的魔石…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.17,0:18:14.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姑且算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.71,0:18:16.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍蓝之月…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.05,0:18:18.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时我查过
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.00,0:18:20.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就是苍月
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.25,0:18:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六花…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.33,0:18:25.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 拜托你了 邪王真眼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.09,0:18:31.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我永远的契约者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.29,0:18:33.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆裂吧 现实
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.94,0:18:35.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绽开吧 神经突触
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.85,0:18:40.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vanishment this world！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.54,0:19:05.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.04,0:19:07.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.11,0:19:09.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 格尔松尼盎斯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.11,0:19:09.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(441,438)\fs21}Ghelzonianses
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.78,0:19:12.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是战争 让我与你的暗炎龙一决胜负
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.64,0:19:13.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用你的全力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.85,0:19:14.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.78,0:19:15.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我终于明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.98,0:19:19.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我应当与之一战的对手 不可不战的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.38,0:19:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是与勇者齐思 共求 同弃的暗炎龙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.73,0:19:26.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是我不可不战的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.14,0:19:29.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我必须决出胜负的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.63,0:19:33.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七宫…我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.22,0:19:35.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是格尔松尼盎斯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.22,0:19:35.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(451,438)\fs21}Ghelzonianses
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.87,0:19:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破坏并重铸世界一切的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.19,0:19:42.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔法魔王少女 期望未来永恒获得魔法的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.35,0:19:44.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就让吾之暗炎龙的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.23,0:19:48.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深深地烙印进你的双目中吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.46,0:19:50.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如我所愿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.16,0:20:15.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗炎龙根本不可能存在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.50,0:20:20.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然更不可能被看见
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.29,0:20:22.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.22,0:20:35.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.34,0:20:37.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.83,0:20:43.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之后 六花的感冒复发倒床不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.34,0:20:47.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇太 我要回溯时空
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.52,0:20:49.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让现在变成7月8日…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.14,0:20:49.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.22,0:20:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背负着崩溃状态的作业 迎来了暑假的结束
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.50,0:20:57.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那样的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.11,0:20:59.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作业写不完啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.59,0:21:01.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦叶长大了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.64,0:21:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦叶也要说话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.29,0:21:07.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果 我还是一次都没去过她们希望我过去的雅加达
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.53,0:21:09.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.29,0:21:12.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的作业没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.89,0:21:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于新生的索菲亚来说这不是什么问题
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.95,0:21:19.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七宫在结束了与暗炎龙的战斗之后
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.89,0:21:22.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成了向新的七宫的进化
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.49,0:21:25.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊 到底什么地方改变了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.40,0:21:29.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不会变的 未来永远我都是魔法魔王少女
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.58,0:21:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以吾以不变之名 将郁集的东西破坏掉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.41,0:21:37.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了保持不变从而需要参加使自己变得强大的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.26,0:21:40.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.19,0:21:42.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是说不定…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.59,0:21:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是连关定则吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.64,0:21:49.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 那就是连关定则哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.70,0:21:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天你也要找天使吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.30,0:21:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.06,0:22:01.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【ED】
